'''布滕博'''（Butembo）是[[剛果民主共和國|剛果民主共和國]]東北部[[北基伍省|北基伍省]]的一座城市，位於[[維龍加國家公園|維龍加國家公園]]西緣，主要農產品有[[茶葉|茶葉]]和[[咖啡|咖啡]]，2019年人口統計共有154,621人<ref name=population/>，下轄{{tsl|en|Bulengera||Bulengera}}、{{tsl|en|Kimemi||Kimemi}}、{{tsl|en|Mususa||Mususa}}與{{tsl|en|Vutamba||Vutamba}}等四個{{tsl|en|List of territories of the Democratic Republic of the Congo|剛果民主共和國小區|小區}}（communes）。

布滕博的居民有超過九成為{{link-fr|南德族|Nande (peuple)}}，過去多以農牧為業，自1980年代起許多人開始投入跨國貿易。布滕博是北基伍省局勢相對穩定的區域<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/monkey-cage/wp/2015/07/31/why-one-city-in-congo-is-astonishingly-stable-and-prosperous/|title=Why one city in Congo is astonishingly stable and prosperous|author=Laura Seay|date=July 31, 2015|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=2019-08-23|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315190732/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/monkey-cage/wp/2015/07/31/why-one-city-in-congo-is-astonishingly-stable-and-prosperous/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2004年，當地曾發起將北基伍省首府從[[戈馬|戈馬]]遷至此的請願活動，但因基礎建設缺乏而被否決<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Economic Empowerment without the State: Lesson from the Nande|url=http://africanajournal.org/wp-content/uploads/Economic-Empowerment-without-the-State-Lesson-from-the-Nandei-AFRICANA-Vol5-No2.pdf|author=Patience Kabamba|journal=''Africana''|volume=5|issue=2|year=2011|access-date=2019-08-23|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305060523/http://africanajournal.org/wp-content/uploads/Economic-Empowerment-without-the-State-Lesson-from-the-Nandei-AFRICANA-Vol5-No2.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
[[File:Hotel_in_Butembo,_Belgian_Congo.jpg|thumb]]
2018年8月，剛果爆發[[2018年－2019年剛果基伍伊波拉出血熱爆發|伊波拉病毒疫情]]，布滕博為受嚴重影響的疫區。當地有謠言指[[伊波拉病毒|伊波拉病毒]]是前來協助防疫的醫護人員所傳入，爆發多起針對治療中心的武裝襲擊，於2019年3月造成一名警員死亡，4月造成[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]派駐當地的一名流行病學家死亡<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nation.co.ke/news/africa/DRC-arrests-11-over-murder-of-doctor/1066-5088758-7r56obz/ |title=DR Congo arrests 11 over murder of doctor fighting Ebola |date=April 26, 2019 |agency=Agence France-Presse |publisher=Daily Nation |location=Nairobi |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808022907/https://www.nation.co.ke/news/africa/DRC-arrests-11-over-murder-of-doctor/1066-5088758-7r56obz/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=AP>{{cite web |url=https://www.voanews.com/a/attackers-kill-doctor-at-hospital-in-congo-s-ebola-epicenter/4883609.html |date=April 19, 2019 |title=Attackers Kill Doctor at Hospital in Congo's Ebola Epicenter |publisher=VOA |agency=Associated Press |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-date=2019-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427031317/https://www.voanews.com/a/attackers-kill-doctor-at-hospital-in-congo-s-ebola-epicenter/4883609.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，對此醫護人員上街遊行抗議，要求當地政府維護其人身安全，否則將集體罷工<ref name=Aizanman0425>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2019/04/25/717079729/why-health-workers-in-the-ebola-hot-zone-are-threatening-to-strike|title=Why Health Workers In The Ebola Hot Zone Are Threatening To Strike|author=Nurith Aizenman|date=2019-04-25|publisher=[[全國公共廣播電台|National Public Radio]]|access-date=2019-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613082058/https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2019/04/25/717079729/why-health-workers-in-the-ebola-hot-zone-are-threatening-to-strike|archive-date=2019-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==設施==
布滕博是{{le|剛果民主共和國空軍|Armed Forces of the Democratic Republic of the Congo}}第二整合旅的駐地<ref>{{tsl|en|MONUSCO|
聯合國駐剛果民主共和國穩定特派團|MONUC}} via Reliefweb, RD Congo : Rapport mensuel des droits de l'homme - juillet 2007</ref>。另外1989年成立的{{link-fr|格拉本天主教大學|Université Catholique du Graben}}（UCG）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ucg-rdc.org/ |title=Université Catholique du Graben (website) |access-date=2019-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190425022552/http://ucg-rdc.org/ |archive-date=2019-04-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>與1979年成立的{{le|魯卡納信徒大學|Adventist University of Lukanga}}（UNILUK）亦位於此地。

